Arslan Multi-Level Parcellation Atlas

Source: R/data.R
arslan.Rd

Brain atlas for the Arslan multi-level parcellation of the cerebral cortex using resting-state fMRI with 50 regions. Contains both 2D polygon geometry for ggseg::geom_brain() and 3D vertex indices for ggseg3d::ggseg3d().

Usage

arslan()

Value

A ggseg.formats::ggseg_atlas object (cortical).

References

Arslan, S., & Rueckert, D. (2015, October). Multi-level parcellation of the cerebral cortex using resting-state fMRI. In International Conference on Medical Image Computing and Computer-Assisted Intervention (pp. 47-54). Springer, Cham. doi:10.1007/978-3-319-24574-4_6
